unctional results show charge localization and ordering. Comparison to\nlow temperature experiments of related compounds suggests that charge\nlocalization is the physically correct result for the hollandite group oxides\nstudied here. . . .\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Sep 2017 14:11:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
